comments: Number of partitions of n if there are two kinds of 2,5,8,11,... and three kinds of 3,6,9,12,... . E.g. a(4)=10 because we have 4, 3+1, 3'+1, 3"+1, 2+2, 2+2', 2'+2', 2+1+1, 2'+1+1, 1+1+1+1. - _Emeric Deutsch_, Mar 23 2005Euler transform of period 3 sequence [1,2,3,1,2,3,...].
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
